### GET ROOMS
## Returns a list of rooms. The result set is scoped
## to the authenticated user's role:
##   - Student -> only the rooms in the school
##   - Teacher -> only the rooms in the school
##   - Local Admin -> only the rooms in the school
##   - Admin -> all rooms across all schools
##
## Response Body (200 OK) - Array of room objects, each containing:
##   - id           (UUID): Unique identifier of the room
##   - name         (string): Name of the room (e.g. "A410")
##   - description  (string): A description (e.g. "Informatikzimmer")
##   - building     (string): Buildin in which the Room is located in
##   - school_id    (string): Unique identifier of the school the room is assigned to
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Returns array of GetRoomResponse objects
##   403 Forbidden - No active session
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
GET {{BASE}}/room
Accept: application/json


### CREATE A ROOM
## Creates a new room.
## Restricted to Local Admin or Admin roles.
##
## Request Body:
##   - name         (string, required): Full room name (e.g. "A410")
##   - description  (string, required): A description (e.g. "Informatikzimmer")
##   - building     (string, required): Buildin in which the Room is located in
##   - school_id    (UUID, optional): UUID of the school; only necessary if a admin creates a room
##
## Responses:
##   201 Created - Room created successfully; returns the new room ID
##   400 Bad Request - Missing required fields or invalid UUID format
##   401 Unauthorized - Insufficient permissions for this role
##   403 Forbidden - No active session
##   404 Not Found - Teacher, class, semester, or school UUID does not exist
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
##
# @name a410
POST {{BASE}}/room
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


{
    "name": "A410",
    "description": "Informatikzimmer",
    "building": "Kraftaum",
    "school_id": "2c64f5d3-4c82-4474-acf6-caa82be28f66"
}


### EDIT A ROOM
## Partially updates an existing room identified by its UUID in the path.
## Only the fields provided in the request body will be updated (PATCH semantics).
## Restricted to Local Admin or Admin roles.
##
## Path Parameter:
##   - {room_id} (UUID): The UUID of the room to update
##
## Request Body (all fields optional - only included fields are updated):
##   - name         (string, optional): New full room name
##   - building     (string, optional): New building
##   - description  (string, optional): New description text
##   - school_id    (UUID, optional): UUID of the school; only necessary if a admin edits a room
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Room updated successfully
##   400 Bad Request - Invalid UUID format or malformed body
##   401 Unauthorized - Insufficient permissions for this role
##   403 Forbidden - No active session
##   404 Not Found - Room UUID does not exist
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
PATCH {{BASE}}/room/{{a410.response.body.resource_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "building": "Gebäude B"
}


### DELETE A ROOM
## Permanently deletes a room identified by its UUID in the path.
## This action is irreversible. 
## Restricted to Local Admin or Admin roles.
##
## Path Parameter:
##   - {room_id} (UUID): The UUID of the room to delete
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Room deleted successfully
##   401 Unauthorized - Insufficient permissions for this role
##   403 Forbidden - No active session
##   404 Not Found - Room UUID does not exist
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
DELETE {{BASE}}/room/{{a410.response.body.resource_id}}
Accept: application/json